          <table class="table">
            <thead>
              <tr class="border-none">
                <th colspan="" class="border-none">
                  <div class="container-fluid d-flex justify-content-start">
                    <div>
                      <img src="/static/images/logo.png" height="80px" width="140px">
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </th>
                <th colspan="3" class="border-none">
                  <div class="container-fluid d-flex justify-content-end align-items-center">
                    <div class="f_14 fw_600">
                      April 2,2024
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </th>
              </tr>
              
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr class="border-none">
                <td colspan="3" class="border-none">
                  <div class="container-fluid d-flex justify-content-center">
                    <div class="f_14 fw_600 text-center">
                      Sub: <u class="fw-bold">Offer of appointment</u>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-none">
                <td colspan="3" class="border-none">
                  <div class="container-fluid d-flex justify-content-start">
                    <div class="f_14 fw-bold">
                      Dear Adhrit
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-none">
                <td colspan="3" class="border-none">
                  <div class="container-fluid d-flex justify-content-start">
                    <div class="f_13 fw_600">
                      This has reference to your application and subsequent discussion with us. We are pleased to offer you an
                      appointment in our organization as
                      Territory Executive – WWA, based out of Kurnool – Andhra Pradesh, on the terms and conditions as have been
                      mutually agreed upon. </div>
                  </div>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-none">
                <td colspan="3" class="border-none">
                  <div class="container-fluid d-flex justify-content-start">
                    <div class="f_13 fw_600">
                      We welcome you to Jubilant Agri & Consumer Products Limited, and look forward to having a happy
                      association. Please sign the duplicate copy of
                      this letter in token of your acceptance and return the same to us </div>
                  </div>
                </td>
              </tr>
        
              <tr class="border-none">
                <td colspan="3" class="border-none">
                  <div class="container-fluid d-flex justify-content-start">
                    <div class="f_13 fw_600">
                      Please note that the cost that will be incurred on account of your joining or reimbursement to you by the
                      company i.e. Relocation Expenses, OneTime Joining Bonus and Notice Pay Reimbursement will be recovered in
                      the full in the event of your leaving the company before completion of 12
                      months of the services in the company.
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </td>
              </tr>
        
              <tr class="border-none">
                <td colspan="3" class="border-none">
                  <div class="container-fluid d-flex justify-content-start">
                    <div class="f_13 fw_600">
                      YIt is understood that our decision to appoint you is based on information provided by you in the
                      application and during the time of interview, you
                      had with us. If, later, the information found to be incorrect, your employment is liable to be terminated
                      without any notice or salary in lieu of
                      notice.
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </td>
              </tr>
        
              <tr class="border-none">
                <td colspan="3" class="border-none">
                  <div class="container-fluid d-flex justify-content-start">
                    <div class="f_13 fw_600">
                      The company reserves the right to verify your documents and background through internal or external
                      agencies. These may include your previous
                      employment history, education/ professional credentials and other background checks. </div>
                  </div>
                </td>
              </tr>
        
              <tr class="border-none">
                <td colspan="3" class="border-none">
                  <div class="container-fluid d-flex justify-content-start">
                    <div class="f_13 fw_600">
                      This offer shall automatically stands withdrawn if we do not receive your acceptance within three days
                      from the date of receipt of offer and your
                      resignation mail within five days from the offer date. </div>
                  </div>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-none">
                <td colspan="3" class="border-none">
                  <div class="container-fluid d-flex justify-content-start">
                    <div class="f_13 fw_600">
