                      verification and authentication
                      of following documents with original that you need to present on the date of joining: -
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-none">
                <td colspan="3" class="border-none">
                  <div class="container-fluid d-flex justify-content-start">
                   <ol class="f_13 fw_600">
                    <li>Pan Card, Aadhar Car, UAN Card from previous employer</li>
                    <li>Photocopies of your educational qualification certificates</li>
                    <li>Four recent passport size photographs</li>
                    <li>Relieving letter from your previous employer with copy of the last pay-slip</li>
                    <li>Certificate for current year income and tax deducted by previous employer.
                    </li>
                    <li>Cancelled cheque with name printed on it.</li>

                   </ol>
                  </div>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-none">
                <td colspan="3" class="border-none">
                  <div class="container-fluid d-flex justify-content-start">
                    <div class="f_13 fw_600">
                      We once again would like to thank you for your interest and hope you will have a fruitful and successful career with us.
<br>Thanking you,
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-none">
                <td colspan="3" class="border-none">
                  <div class="container-fluid d-flex justify-content-start">
                    <div class="f_13 fw_600">
                      For<span class="fw-bold"> Jubilant Agri & Consumer Products Ltd.</span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-none">
                <td colspan="" class="border-none">
                  <div class="container-fluid d-flex justify-content-start">
                    <div class="f_13 fw-bold">
                      Amit Roy Chowdhury<br>
                      DGM – Human Resources 
                                            </div>
                  </div>
                </td>
                <td colspan="2" class="border-none">
                  <div class="container-fluid d-flex justify-content-start">
                    <div class="f_13 fw-bold">
                      Rohit Jain<br>
                      DGM – FP&A
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
            <tfoot>
              
              <tr class="border-none">
                <td colspan="3" class="border-none">
                  <div class="container-fluid d-flex justify-content-start">
                    <div class="f_14 fw-bold t_b">
